                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "measured-mix",
                    "text": "Main path: measured additions with frequent checks."
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "pilot-mix",
                    "text": "Alternate path: run a small pilot batch first."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "measured-mix",
            "text": "Dissolve baking soda in measured water, add vinegar dropwise, and keep splashes inside a spill tray. Pause if heat or foaming spikes.",
